|               |         TableScan: hits projection=[WatchID, ClientIP, IsRefresh, ResolutionWidth]                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
| physical_plan | BytesProcessedExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                            |
|               |   SchemaCastScanExec                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |
|               |     VirtualExecutionPlan name=duckdb compute_context=:memory: initial_sql=SELECT "hits"."WatchID", "hits"."ClientIP", count(1) AS "c", sum("hits"."IsRefresh"), avg("hits"."ResolutionWidth") FROM "hits" GROUP BY "hits"."WatchID", "hits"."ClientIP" ORDER BY "c" DESC NULLS FIRST LIMIT 10 |
